==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*εὑρίσκω / heuriskō / hyoo-ris'-ko
*A prolonged form of a primary word εὕρω heurō; which (together with another cognate form, εὑρέω heureō) is used for it in all the tenses except the present and imperfect; to find (literally or figuratively): 

===Verb===
'''εὑρίσκω'''

# To [[find]], [[get]], [[obtain]], [[perceive]], [[see]].

